This light filled Mid-Century home nestled on Foothill Blvd near Backdoor Bakery, Oro Vista Park, Tujunga Wash, Descanso Garden Spa, Los Angeles National Forest Hiking and Equestrian Trails! This bright & spacious one-story home sits back from the street & features: 2 bedrooms, adjacent to 1 beautifully remodeled bathroom, and 1 large step-down double height ceiling bedroom/office w/ concrete fls. The recently remodeled kitchen opens to dining rm and features quartz countertops, & newer appliances. The living rm has two walls of vintage glass windows, wood floors & a decorative fireplace. There is an amazing large Sunroom that is a perfect art studio/ great room, that connects to a 2-car garage & a long driveway. The house comes with unique vintage touches & all the desirable modern amenities, HVAC system, EV car charger, 200-amp electrical panel. The front & back yard are beautifully environmentally landscaped w/decomposed granite, and low-maintenance native plants & mountain views.

A terraced oasis, privately perched high above the street with ample space and striking panoramic views of downtown and the surrounding hills of North East Los Angeles. Upon entry, be greeted by an elegantly open and airy lounging room and kitchen, perfect for entertaining or dining in with the family. Carrera marble and fresh hardwood flooring ease the eyes throughout while an abundance of dual paned glass help welcome in plenty of natural light.Upstairs you'll find three well proportioned bedrooms, including a giant primary suite featuring a spa-style bathroom with dual vanity sinks, proper walk-in closet as well as a private balcony. Below at the street level, a mighty 700 sq ft garage with 14 ft+ high ceilings suggests real potential for an incredible work space or artist's studio. All while being located just minutes from the various bars, cafes and venues that York and Figueroa have to offer (Gold Line, Cafe Birdie, Lodge Room, Joy etc..), you can live in peace AND be in the mix.

Classic Spanish style home that has been updated and remodeled but still retains all the original charm. Living room opens to the remodeled kitchen with custom cabinets and counters and high-end appliances. Both bathrooms were completely redone and there is a separate laundry room with extra storage. Primary bedroom has French doors that lead out to the deck. Other feature include skylights, central heat and air conditioning, full home alarm system with wired screens, hardwood floors, copper plumbing, and new gas line. Two car garage with an extra storeroom. Large back yard with plenty of room for a pool, an ADU, or a garden. Excellent central West Los Angeles location close to shopping, restaurants, and the Expo line.

Amazing Storybook 3 bed/3 bath home in Colfax Meadows with pool and guest house! Charming oozes from this house with a flexible floor plan to fit many different needs. Let me talk you through it before I walk you through it: you enter through the front door into the living room, and off to the left is a bedroom with a private bath. Past the living room is a connected dining room and kitchen which leads to a large great room and a magnificent yard with a pool and guest house. Off the dining room is a second bedroom which shares a bath with the great room, and stairs that lead up to the primary bedroom with private sittinrg room and/or office and just completed master bath. Back to the yard, there is a guest house which was used as a music studio, so it's soundproofed! A beautiful pool and patio complete the picture of this great compound in the Carpenter School District, walking distance to Tujunga Village shops and restaurants.

Must see.. This elegant, traditional two-story home offers impressive attention to detail with unique style and coastal classical charm. Welcome guests in the grand entryway that opens to a beautiful, spacious Living and dining space. Master suite with custom closet in the heart of Westchester. One of a kind Beautiful home on large lot with endless possibilities. OPEN SUNDAY July 18th 1-4pm

Bright and inviting Mar Vista modern farmhouse on a quiet, tree-lined street! Come see this meticulously remodeled four bed, three bath home in a highly sought-after Westside neighborhood. With vaulted ceilings and an open floor plan, this house has wonderful light and cheery ambiance. The bedrooms are spacious and the primary has an enviable walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. The kitchen is a chefs dream with a large center island, ample storage and marble countertops. Situated on a large 7,131sqft lot, owners and their guests will enjoy indoor/outdoor entertaining including a bocce ball court and newly landscaped private backyard. Enjoy the Serena & Lily meets Amber Interior vibe!
